{"tid":2022920,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"［極罕］鄭家純船P照流出 多名成員曝光","createTime":"2020-05-18T15:23:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-18T15:25:20.000Z","uid":185651,"like":8,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f134e352f2ec6698e514cbd8fa985edad4dffb33","tid":2022920,"uid":185651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T15:23:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/fin/20200518/s00010/8d35226cd8447cb9b857dd82b80e475c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2F20200518%2Fs00010%2F8d35226cd8447cb9b857dd82b80e475c.jpg&h=de8d83f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\nImage 1 of 1 - 左起鄭志雯、葉美卿、鄭家純、鄭志亮、余雅穎及鄭志剛。(鄭志雯IG圖片)<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style=\"color: red;\">極罕！平時要睇「大孖沙」全家福真係唔容易，不過今日新世界（0017）執董鄭志雯（Sonia）就係Ig（Instagram）上載了一家六口遊船河的相任睇，非常益大家！</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n今次鄭氏家族的船河照非常珍貴，事關就連集團巨無霸項目Victoria Dockside開幕都無張咁齊人的相。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n相中除了大家不時見到的Sonia爹哋、新世界主席鄭家純（純官）、大哥兼執行副主席兼行政總裁鄭志剛（Adrian），連一向好少同場的媽咪葉美卿、細細佬鄭志亮（Christopher）兼大嫂余雅穎（Jennifer）都一齊現身，齊齊坐遊艇食生果，非常溫馨。不過另一細佬鄭志明（Brian）就未有出現，唔通係佢負責揸機?<br />\r\n<br />\r\n相片中鄭氏一家都笑意迎迎，惟獨純官繼續COOL樣，不過最令人驚訝係Sonia媽咪葉美卿愈睇愈年輕，拍住Sonia猶如姐妹花！而不知Adrian係咪近排出得海多，連一向白白淨的都曬黑咗呢。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<a href=\"https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1589803854665&amp;issue=20200518\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpfinance.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1589803854665%26issue%3D20200518&d=pzZXWUTiTgu0UE2nVnCkCj4xCSFqVWWaKp6LAuIW5iI%3D&h=95518ef4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1589803854665&amp;issue=20200518</a>"},{"pid":"2f156f800e4e54c0cb1249fce2e195359eeb1b99","tid":2022920,"uid":266467,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T15:25:20.000Z","msg":"屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"2f156f800e4e54c0cb1249fce2e195359eeb1b99","tid":2022920,"uid":266467,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T15:25:20.000Z","msg":"屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}}